      "\n",
      "\n",
      "Namaste! Mere aapke liye kuch schemes hai jo aapke liye eligible hai.\n",
      "\n",
      "Aapka income 1.8 lakh hai, aap Uttar Pradesh se hai aur aap kisaan hai. Yeh schemes aapke liye eligible hai:\n",
      "\n",
      "1. Ayushman Bharat: Aapko free health insurance milta hai, jismein 5 lakh tak ka expense nahi karna padta.\n",
      "2. PM Kisan Samman Nidhi: Aapko yearly 6,000 rupees ki income support milta hai, kyunki aap kisaan hai.\n",
      "3. Ujjwala Yojana: Yeh scheme ladkiyon ke liye hai, lekin aapko bhi free LPG connection mil sakti hai.\n",
      "\n",
      "Note: Other schemes like PM Awas Yojana and National Social Assistance Programme are not eligible for you as your income is above the limit.\n",
      "\n",
      "Yeh schemes aapke liye kafi helpful ho sakti hai. Aapko yeh schemes ke bare mein aur jankari chahiye, to aapko kahaan jana chahiye?\n",
      "\n",
      "Translation:\n",
      "Hello! I have some schemes that are eligible for you.\n",
      "\n",
      "Your income is 1.8 lakh, you are from Uttar Pradesh, and you are a farmer. These schemes are eligible for you:\n",
      "\n",
      "1. Ayushman Bharat: You will get free health insurance, where you won't have to pay for expenses up to 5 lakh.\n",
      "2. PM Kisan Samman Nidhi: You will get yearly income support of 6,000 rupees, because you are a farmer.\n",
      "3. Ujjwala Yojana: This scheme is for women, but you can also get a free LPG connection.\n",
      "\n",
      "Note: Other schemes like PM Awas Yojana and National Social Assistance Programme are not eligible for you as your income is above the limit.\n",
      "\n",
      "These schemes can be very helpful for you. If you want more information about these schemes, where should you go?\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "from eligibility_engine import find_eligible_schemes\n",
    "from ai_engine import explain_schemes\n",
    "\n",
    "profile = {\n",
    "\"income\":180000,\n",
    "\"state\":\"Uttar Pradesh\",\n",
    "\"occupation\":\"farmer\"\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "schemes = find_eligible_schemes(profile)\n",
    "\n",
    "result = explain_schemes(profile, schemes)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(result)"
   ]
